    <item>
      <title>马斯克拒绝透露他是否仍致力于开发更便宜的特斯拉电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/musk-refuses-to-say-if-he-s-still-committed-to-cheaper-tesla-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克不想谈论他是否致力于将低成本电动汽车推向市场，也不想谈论这家汽车制造商过去几个月的艰难处境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/musk-refuses-to-say-if-he-s-still-committed-to-cheaper-tesla-evs</guid>
